{"tid":1989214,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[直播] 梁繼平談現今香港政局","createTime":"2020-04-25T18:30:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T03:47:24.000Z","uid":70063,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7c2e9fc8fdf71cb3597d9736ebe78987371a7b7d","tid":1989214,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:30:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lionrock.cafe/videos/1509574405870797/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flionrock.cafe%2Fvideos%2F1509574405870797%2F&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=17970b50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lionrock.cafe/videos/1509574405870797/</a>"},{"pid":"945e30ea7fbe5aee9df110796922e233a3dd7939","tid":1989214,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:32:19.000Z","msg":"暴徒博士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261ace4d45c50b3c0aa7b12cb70884802cc0e48b","tid":1989214,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:32:37.000Z","msg":"Brian Leung Kai-Ping, 梁繼平, a Hongkonger and Political Science PhD student at University of Washington; one of the writers of A Discourse on HK Nationalism (香港民族論).<br />\n<br />\nOn 1 July 2019, hundreds of protesters stormed into The Legislative Council Complex. Brian was one of them, and he was the only one who took off his mask, made a speech and asked more protesters to join them: &quot;We Hongkongers, have nothing left to lose.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nIn spring 2020, he is back to a normal international student, staying at the campus of UW, drinking his coffee (not Starbucks, I asked) and working on his PhD thesis. What has he changed in the past ten months? What has he learnt from the United States? What is his thought on the recent Basic Law Article 22 issue?<br />\n<br />\nLet's grind it out.<br />\n<br />\nMore information about:<br />\nBrian Leung:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.latimes.com/world/asia/la-fg-hong-kong-unmasked-protester-identity-dissent-20190706-story.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fla-fg-hong-kong-unmasked-protester-identity-dissent-20190706-story.html&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=01c5bcd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.latimes.com/world/asia/la-fg-hong-kong-unmasked-protester-identity-dissent-20190706-story.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n3EsrjpgKbQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dn3EsrjpgKbQ&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=d3889b1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n3EsrjpgKbQ</a><br />\nThe Basic Law Article 22 issue: <br />\n<a href=\"https://hongkongfp.com/2020/04/21/just-in-mainland-affairs-minister-patrick-nip-replaced-following-apology-over-beijing-office-row/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhongkongfp.com%2F2020%2F04%2F21%2Fjust-in-mainland-affairs-minister-patrick-nip-replaced-following-apology-over-beijing-office-row%2F&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=145754f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hongkongfp.com/2020/04/21/just-in-mainland-affairs-minister-patrick-nip-replaced-following-apology-over-beijing-office-row/</a>"},{"pid":"0605c0a9c907e442bc5eb41585eb280988078202","tid":1989214,"uid":247494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T18:36:15.000Z","msg":"白兵：笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bdbccdd2c3e38fe2d594c8ef3d7dd2499556fe","tid":1989214,"uid":185606,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T19:31:02.000Z","msg":"白兵都係去賣返樓算"},{"pid":"38c81cf1ab6ca1e3ba094426d4aedb4c88ba5546",